ONLY THE LOOK IS LIGHTER ( JT )
By ANNE-MARIE SCHIRO c.1998 N.Y .
Times News Service
NEW YORK _ Once June arrives , those indispensable leather tote bags look awfully heavy .
It is definitely time to switch to fabric or straw .
In Henri Bendel 's private-label collection are natural straw totes ( $ 68 ) and woven straw totes that are lined in green or lavender ( $ 78 ) .
The A/X Armani Exchange , 568 Broadway ( Prince Street ) , has a two-compartment straw tote with brown leather handles ( $ 68 ) .
Bergdorf Goodman has totes in patterned canvas , natural straw or woven plastic by Kate Spade ( $ 75 to $ 195 ) , flower-trimmed straw totes by Rafe ( $ 185 ) and an embroidered cotton tote by CK Calvin Klein ( $ 48 ) .
Barneys New York has see-through mesh totes by Miu Miu ( $ 230 ) , crocheted plastic bags by Tote le Monde ( $ 145 ) and plaid cotton bags by Pixie Yates ( $ 135 ) .
Saks Fifth Avenue has flower-trimmed straw bags by Kate Spade ( $ 160 ) and Rafe ( $ 175 ) , woven pink plastic by Inca ( $ 55 ) and a private-label straw with wooden handles ( $ 100 ) .
